# Landing Page Plan

Sections (order): Navbar → Hero → Built-at logos → Learn → Solve → No code → Loved by → CTA band → Footer.

Primitives:

- `Section` (outer spacing)
- `GradientPanel` (hero/pastel panel backgrounds)
- `BrowserFrame` (screenshot frame)

Components:

- `Navbar`, `Hero`, `LogoStrip`, `LearnSection`, `SolveSection`, `NoCodeSection`, `TestimonialsSection`, `CtaBand`, `Footer`

Styling:

- Typography: `font-geist` + `text-h1|h2|h3|body|body2`, `leading-none`
- Colors: text `text-primary-black|dark-gray`, panels `bg-secondary-*`, CTA `rounded-cta shadow-cta`

Grids:

- Features: `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3`
- Testimonials: two rows of `md:grid-cols-3`

Data:

- Centralize copy in `src/content/sections.ts` for features, testimonials, footer links
